No. D-2612. In the Matter of Discipline of Sol Zalel Rosen. 565 U.S. 1053, 132 S. Ct. 810,

181 L. Ed. 2d 521,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 8413. November 28, 2011.

Sol Zalel Rosen, of Arlington, Virginia, is suspended from the practice of law in this Court and a rule will issue, returnable within 40 days, requiring him to show cause why he should not be disbarred from the practice of law in this Court.
